high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wooden dresser on the right.
Close the lid on the laptop computer and pick it up from the dresser.
Turn around and hang a right at the wall to reach the nightstand next to the bed.
Turn on the small lamp on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a laptop computer by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk up to the bed, then turn right and walk over to the dresser.
Close the laptop that is sitting on the dresser and pick it up.
Turn around completely, walk across the room, then turn right and walk up to the nightstand.
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a laptop using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and go toward the bed, then turn right and go to the dresser.
Pick up the computer on top of the dresser.
Turn around and go to the wall, then turn right and go forward to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the computer in the lamp light.
